Struct swc_core::ecma::utils::swc_common::pass::Optional

pub struct Optional<V> {
    pub enabled: bool,
    pub visitor: V,
}
Available on crate features __ecma and __utils only.
Expand description

A visitor which visits node only if enabled is true.
